{"tid":873412,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗 山卡啦 - 尚悅．嶺 開價，平均15800/呎","createTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T13:01:25.000Z","uid":62935,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"116ae00a1b59c033ce6660255241ca8331ee435e","tid":873412,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:02:12.000Z","msg":"由恒地牽頭發展的元朗尚悅‧嶺-蝶翠峰第五期今日中午上載樓書，旋即公布首張價單。項目首張價單101伙，實用面積由195至370平方呎。價單定價介乎327.5萬至632.2萬，價單呎價介乎14,862至18,108元。用盡折扣，折實400萬內單位有15伙，最平要約317.67萬起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n檢視圖片<br />\n<br />\n若選用120付款計劃，買家最高可以享用3%折扣，折實價介乎約317.6575萬至613.234萬，折實呎價介乎14,416至17,564。<br />\n<br />\n折實樓價平過400萬有15伙，包括首批全數195平方單位，以及數伙面積266平方呎單位，入場單位為1座2樓K室，實用面積195平方呎，定價327.5萬，呎價約16,795，扣除折扣，折實價317.76575萬，折實呎價約16,291元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恆基係咪傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想突擊開價 但 貴過朗屏站？"},{"pid":"59b1154e814eb96db263d7b300aedca4269c8631","tid":873412,"uid":59746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"四叔向來高水"},{"pid":"721295370413c197b9f7397114c1efa83a7b8305","tid":873412,"uid":36724,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"一萬八千幾蚊呎都係得370呎的單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個位仲咁鬼遠市中心/鐵路站"},{"pid":"ecebad0c6cd7abe556656065d59780f3feea7c1a","tid":873412,"uid":35941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:06:41.000Z","msg":"競猜賣得多唔多過40%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1184764b46216ee7b10fc2c0cf7cfe0852817078","tid":873412,"uid":164283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"諗住lump sum 細，易d搵水魚落搭掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\